<p>Okay, now that the Hello World sequence is complete, I feel more comfortable reading this one.</p>
<p>Which leads to the question, when exactly does this fit into the timeline established by Hello World? Because unless I'm misunderstanding something, this MTF wasn't formed until the express purpose of reacting to the Maxwellist thing, which and then they events of Hello World happened pretty much immediately before culminating in such a way as to preclude the presence of one of the characters presented here<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-669709-1" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-669709-1')">1</a></sup>.</p>
<p>I like this story, but I'm confused by the timeline.</p>
